[{"id":"ef23256079dea70a5e76ddcf2510d2a0","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Emad Hanna","to_list":[{"name":"Emad Hanna","email":"ehanna@nysgmail.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: Your album has been shared!","date":"2008-03-14T11:12:54.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 14, 2008","formatted_time":"11:12 AM","body":"yes\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Emad Hanna <ehanna@nysgmail.com>\nTo: jeeproject@yahoo.com\nSent: Thursday, March 13, 2008 8:11:57 PM\nSubject: FW: Your album has been shared!\n\n\nJeffrey,\nHere are some landscaping pictures and pictures of the new boat from ProKat and the enclosure being installed on Midnight Express.\nI need to send $ 30,000 from the owed balance of $ 81,500. May I go ahead and wire the funds?\nThank you\nSubject: LSJ Landscaping and Boats \n \n\nIf you can't see the pictures in this email, click here to see it in a web browser:\nhttp://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.1y1fu48m&x=0&y=-g2v9r1 \n\n\n \n\nEmad has shared photos with you.\n\n\n\nLSJ and Boat\n(1 album) \nYou're invited to view my online photos at the Gallery. Enjoy! \n- Emad\n \nView photos  \n\n\nDo more with these photos! \n\nBuy Kodak prints Create a collage Create a mini photo book Create mugs \n\n \n \n \n \n\n\n \n\n\n \n\nQuestions? Visit http://www.kodakgallery.com/Help.jsp.\n\u00a9Kodak, 2008. All rights reserved. \n\n","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">yes<BR><BR>\n<DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">----- Original Message ----<BR>From: Emad Hanna &lt;ehanna@nysgmail.com&gt;<BR>To: jeeproject@yahoo.com<BR>Sent: Thursday, March 13, 2008 8:11:57 PM<BR>Subject: FW: Your album has been shared!<BR><BR>\n<STYLE>\n<!--\n\ndiv.view a:hover {\ncolor:#f80;}\ndiv